Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please revoke my guard orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have something important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:56.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What if I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:01:59.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...there is something more important than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is your passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:17.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The real you,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your past,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:19.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Ein.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:40.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:45.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was no way we could have known...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the destiny that awaited us from then on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can take a look, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:00.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you afraid to reclaim your past?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:07.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have been killing people at the organization's demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, you've rendered such brilliant services.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...because I have neither memory nor past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:22.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were following orders like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You felt no sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:32.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you return to your old self...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:35.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...the guilt of your sins may haunt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what you're afraid of, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:45.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that's the reason why I want you to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:00.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Distance, 249 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Intermittent wind from the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Return to the real you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:14.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...while accepting all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The identity as Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You people took my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and stained these hands with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:29.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The organization is about to be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:41.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zwei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:48.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But no matter your competence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:52.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want a mere puppet that follows orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What I want is a comrade in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A subordinate I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone who would follow me of his own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once I know my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.12,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I... I'm not sure I can be myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it comes to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My mission is to back up the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:40.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These are my targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What organization are they with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The cargo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A sniper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not yet, Aniki. {Aniki = big brother}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.12,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:05.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:11.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To pin us down like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They sure have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try saying your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Azuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you've remembered it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...on a trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So many people... with these hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I only...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...wanted to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It would have been better if I had not remembered anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want a mere puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must wake from your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Return to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The past and the sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:50.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Accept and face them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Through your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe, that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Follow me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:27.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are people here that need your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is your destined place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:35.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're willing to stain those hands further with more blood and follow me carrying your sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:39.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can promise you a wonderful world. {genjitsu=reality, but funi translated it as "future". feel free to edit it whatever you like.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:39.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is not coercion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have one more option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Another...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Another option...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Return... to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it is what you truly wish for,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can arrange it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You might doubt me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would really return you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to your hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is a subordinate with a strong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You idiot! What're you doing shooting your own people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care if it's Scythe's order,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}stop being a puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't have anywhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Think it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:10:00.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That snake bastard is just using you as a sacrificial pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Return...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:26.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}This is a big decision for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I can give you time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Think this over by yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, Azuma speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no way I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...ever return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:41.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:11.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That bastard Scythe has done it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you heard how many casualties we incurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:20.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He will get just what he deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...Phantom as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you here to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:53.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You haven't heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:04.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then hurry up and get back to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are still able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sudden change of plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe has betrayed the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He used Phantom to attack Inferno's cargo hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe went into hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and Phantom has escaped as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She took a bullet from Lizzie, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The organization is currently looking for them with all its manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neither have been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They suspect you too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can prove where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is no more time to deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to make a choice soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come to my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:03.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I need to tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both Scythe and Phantom are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:13.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you choose to side with them, the organization will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The bleeding won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The bullet is still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need to find a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The hospitals have probably been compromised by the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All escape routes have been blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They are like caged birds now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They can't flee from the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not even Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:31.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The only thing left is choosing the predator for the prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:45.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You still can't find them even after looking for them with so many men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The freeways? Block them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:49.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only I'd killed her back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Clau, what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's Scythe's pet dog as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chances are he goes over to their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If that happens, Lizzie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will be the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss McCunnen gave me a passport tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I remembered everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I remembered my name as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My name is Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:52.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a lot better than the crude "Zwei", isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...it didn't really make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:13.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm no longer the me from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a human that isn't supposed to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do I have no choice but to return to the organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:24.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you return with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:30.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Both Scythe and Phantom are our enemies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}If you choose to side with them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}the organization will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}...kill you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:39.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we return, Ein will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:44.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leaving Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and returning by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:07.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:14.42,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Don't mind me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}The wind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:27.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Blue, white and green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}That's all that's left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}The rest is a place of emptiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}But it's so bright and dazzling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}The wind blows...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}A really strong wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Ein.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}You too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We, having no names...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...only followed our orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:11.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were used as pawns and discarded afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't mess with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:16.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't mess with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Such a meaningless life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.12,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:35.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The only one to protect you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will never hand you over to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's run together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:46.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:37.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll give you a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:41.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not like Phantom or a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:43.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your name.
